resources.resid-settings-signOutConfirmationText:
Ese koko urashaka kuvanamo muri iyi porogaramu konti yawe ya Microsoft, ndetse n'amakuru yayo yose?

Nta foto n'imwe yawe ndetse na videwo biri busibwe, ariko ntibizongera kugaragara muri iyi porogaramu.

resources.residConnectUpsellFlyoutText: Ushobora kureba amafoto na videwo byo ku bikoresho byawe, serivisi, ndetse n'imbuga mpuzambaga byose mu mwanya umwe.  Kugira ngo utangire, reba neza ko uri kuri internet .
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_EmptySourceView: Inkomoko zose z'amafoto yawe zirahishwe. Kugira ngo ugaragaze zimwe, hindura igenamiterere ryawe.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_GenericDevice:
Porogaramu y'amafoto ikwereka amafoto na videwo byo ku bikoresho byawe byose mu mwanya umwe.

Kugira ngo urebe amafoto na videwo byo ku yindi PC jya kuri iyo PC, jya kuri SkyDrive.com/windows, kugira ngo ukurure kandi winjizemo Microsoft SkyDrive .Noneho winjire ukoresheje konti yawe ya Microsoft kandi urebe neza ko ituma mbasha kubona dosiye ziri aho ariho hose igenamiterere.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Device: Niba hari amafoto uhafite, reba neza niba wayashyize mu isomero ry'amafoto yawe rya  {{%1}}.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Service: Kongera amwe mu mafoto kuri konti yawe kugira ngo utangire.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_SkyDrive:
SkyDrive iguha ububiko bw'ubuntu kuri Interineti ubikamo amafoto, videwo n'inyandiko ku buryo ushobora kubigeraho aho waba uri hose.

Kugira ngo utangire jya kuri SkyDrive.com amafoto na videwo zose uzabikaho bizagaragara hano. Amafoto na videwo byose ahabika biragaragara hano.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_PicturesLibrary:
Kugira ngo utangire, huzaho igikoresho nyongera (kamera, telefoni, disiki igendanwa n'ibindi) hanyuma uzane cyangwa ukoporore amafoto cyangwa videwo mu isomero ryawe ry'amafoto

niba wari usanzwe ufite amafoto cyangwa videwo kuri iyi PC, reba neza ko biri mu isomero ryawe ry'amafoto.Ushobora gutungaya isomero ryawe ry'amafoto muri mugenzuzi ya dosiye.
